            ## Github repositories

            * [Sample frontend application](https://github.com/oskariorg/sample-application) that you can use as an example to build your own Oskari-based apps
            * [Sample server application](https://github.com/oskariorg/sample-server-extension) that you can use as an example to build your own Oskari-based server
            * [Oskari JavaScript framework](https://github.com/oskariorg/oskari-frontend)
            * [Oskari Server](https://github.com/oskariorg/oskari-server)
            * [Sample configurations](https://github.com/oskariorg/sample-configs)
            * [RPC client library](https://github.com/oskariorg/rpc-client)
            * [Oskari.org site](https://github.com/oskariorg/oskari-docs)

            Master branch has stable production ready code that is in use for example at ​[Demo.oskari.org](https://demo.oskari.org) and ​[Paikkatietoikkuna.fi](https://kartta.paikkatietoikkuna.fi).

            Develop branch has the most recent code which is more of a work in progress and may contain bugs and is in use in for [Dev.oskari.org](https://dev.oskari.org).

